data.description: Captivating two-story pool home in the heart of the highly sought after neighborhood of Shenandoah. Motivated Seller. Bring all offers. On a spacious corner lot, find privacy in the fenced backyard oasis with a pool, jacuzzi, and tiki hut. Enjoy peace of mind with a new roof, hurricane impact windows, doors, and garage door, complemented by stylish zebra blinds. The kitchen and family room create a perfect blend of comfort and entertainment. Your walk-in closets and ample storage add to the convenience.  Fantastic neighborhood with it's parks, playgrounds, lakes and tree-shaded walking paths offers easy access to I-595 & I-75, with top-rated schools nearby. Make this your haven of tranquility, where style meets security. Welcome to the perfect blend of comfort and convenience!
